  m_Name: Memory Rules
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Sentence
  id: MemoryRules
  text: It's pretty simple! You just pick two cards, and if they match, you take
    the cards out! So it's best to try and get all of the cards out in as few moves
    as possible, so make sure you remember where they are! Does that sound fun?
  nextSentence: {fileID: 0}
